        public int checkTree(BinarySearchTree<java.lang.Integer> tree)
        checkTree method Takes a Binary Search Tree. Checks whether it is an AVL tree, or a RB tree, or any of them. If tree is an AVL tree and a RB tree, returns 0. If the tree is only an AVL tree, returns 1. If the tree is only a RB tree, returns 2. If the tree is any of them, returns 3.
